
---

### 3. `.env.example` (new file – place in project root)
```env
# Version Control System
VCS_TOKEN=your_github_token
VCS_REPO=owner/repo

# LLM Provider
LLM_API_KEY=your_gemini_or_openai_key
LLM_PROVIDER=gemini        # or "openai"
LLM_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash

# Optional Slack
SLACK_TOKEN=xoxb-your-slack-token
SLACK_CHANNEL=#deploy-approvals

# Database
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./app.db

# CI (if different from VCS)
CI_TOKEN=
CI_URL=

# Webhook secret (for GitHub)
WEBHOOK_SECRET=

# Polling interval (seconds)
POLL_INTERVAL=60

# Debug mode
DEBUG=false